msgstr "फोटो, ब्याज र प्रोमो ब्यानर"

#: core/views.py:59
msgid "Installable app (PWA) for guests & staff"
msgstr "पाहुना र कर्मचारीका लागि इन्स्टल गर्न मिल्ने एप (PWA)"

#: core/views.py:60
msgid "3 team members"
msgstr "३ टोली सदस्य"

#: core/views.py:62
msgid "VIP"
msgstr "VIP"

#: core/views.py:63
msgid "For venues that want full brand ownership and a bigger team."
msgstr "पूर्ण ब्रान्ड स्वामित्व र ठूलो टोली चाहने स्थलहरूका लागि।"

#: core/views.py:64 templates/marketing/_contact.html:5
msgid "Talk to us"
msgstr "हामीसँग कुरा गर्नुहोस्"

#: core/views.py:65
msgid "Everything in Business"
msgstr "Business का सबै सुविधा"

#: core/views.py:66
msgid "Custom domain — menu.yourrestaurant.com"
msgstr "कस्टम डोमेन — menu.yourrestaurant.com"

#: core/views.py:67
msgid "Your venue as its own branded app"
msgstr "तपाईंको स्थल आफ्नै ब्रान्डेड एपका रूपमा"

#: core/views.py:68
msgid "Unlimited team + branch-scoped managers"
msgstr "असीमित टोली + शाखा-स्तरका म्यानेजर"

#: core/views.py:69
msgid "Priority WhatsApp support"
msgstr "प्राथमिकता WhatsApp सहयोग"

#: core/views.py:117
msgid "Please fill in your name, venue name and phone number."
msgstr "कृपया आफ्नो नाम, स्थलको नाम र फोन नम्बर भर्नुहोस्।"

#: templates/home.html:3
msgid "Gaamos — QR menus & live orders for cafés, restaurants and bars"
msgstr "Gaamos — क्याफे, रेस्टुरेन्ट र बारका लागि QR मेनु र लाइभ अर्डर"

#: templates/marketing/_contact.html:6
msgid "Tell us about your venue"
msgstr "आफ्नो स्थलबारे हामीलाई बताउनुहोस्"

#: templates/marketing/_contact.html:7
msgid ""
"Leave a request and a Gaamos representative will reach out within one "
"business day — we'll walk you through setup, pricing, and getting your first "
"QR on the table."
msgstr ""
"अनुरोध छोड्नुहोस्, Gaamos प्रतिनिधिले एक कार्य दिनभित्र सम्पर्क गर्नेछन् — सेटअप, मूल्य र "
"पहिलो QR टेबलमा राख्ने काममा हामी तपाईंलाई साथ दिनेछौं।"

#: templates/marketing/_contact.html:9
msgid "Fill in the request"
msgstr "अनुरोध भर्नुहोस्"

#: templates/marketing/_contact.html:10
msgid "We call you back"
msgstr "हामी तपाईंलाई फोन गर्छौं"

#: templates/marketing/_contact.html:11
msgid "Your menu goes live"
msgstr "तपाईंको मेनु लाइभ हुन्छ"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_form.html:7
msgid "Your name"
msgstr "तपाईंको नाम"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_form.html:8
msgid "Suman Thapa"
msgstr "सुमन थापा"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_form.html:11
msgid "Venue name"
msgstr "स्थलको नाम"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_form.html:12
msgid "Momo Ghar Café"
msgstr "मःमः घर क्याफे"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_form.html:17
msgid "Phone"
msgstr "फोन"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_form.html:21
msgid "Email"
msgstr "इमेल"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_form.html:26
msgid "Venue type"
msgstr "स्थलको प्रकार"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_form.html:36
msgid "What do you need?"
msgstr "तपाईंलाई के चाहिन्छ?"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_form.html:37
msgid "e.g. 2 branches, ~60 menu items, table ordering…"
msgstr "जस्तै: 2 शाखा, ~60 मेनु आइटम, टेबल अर्डरिङ…"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_form.html:43
msgid "Request a callback"
msgstr "कलब्याक अनुरोध गर्नुहोस्"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_form.html:44
msgid "We'll only use your details to contact you about Gaamos."
msgstr "तपाईंको विवरण Gaamos बारे सम्पर्क गर्न मात्र प्रयोग गर्नेछौं।"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_success.html:4
msgid "Request received!"
msgstr "अनुरोध प्राप्त भयो!"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_success.html:5
msgid ""
"Thanks — a Gaamos representative will contact you within one business day."
msgstr "धन्यवाद — Gaamos प्रतिनिधिले एक कार्य दिनभित्र तपाईंलाई सम्पर्क गर्नेछन्।"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_success.html:7
msgid "Send another request"
msgstr "अर्को अनुरोध पठाउनुहोस्"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:4 templates/marketing/_footer.html:12
#: templates/marketing/_nav.html:6
msgid "Features"
msgstr "सुविधाहरू"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:5
msgid "Everything a busy venue needs. Nothing it doesn't."
msgstr "व्यस्त स्थललाई चाहिने सबै कुरा। नचाहिने केही पनि होइन।"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:11
msgid "Menu Builder"
msgstr "मेनु बिल्डर"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:12
msgid "Build your menu in minutes, not weekends"
msgstr "मेनु मिनेटमै बनाउनुहोस्, हप्तौं होइन"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:13
msgid ""
"Start from a global library of dishes and drinks — tick the ones you serve, "
"drop them into categories, set your prices, add photos. Your menu is live "
"before your coffee gets cold."
msgstr ""
"परिकार र पेय पदार्थको साझा लाइब्रेरीबाट सुरु गर्नुहोस् — आफूले बेच्ने छान्नुहोस्, श्रेणीहरूमा "
"राख्नुहोस्, मूल्य तोक्नुहोस्, फोटो थप्नुहोस्। कफी सेलाउनुअघि नै तपाईंको मेनु लाइभ हुन्छ।"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:15
msgid "Template library of ready-made items"
msgstr "तयार आइटमहरूको टेम्प्लेट लाइब्रेरी"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:16
msgid "Drag-and-drop categories and groups"
msgstr "तानेर राख्न मिल्ने श्रेणी र समूह"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:17
msgid "Clone a menu from another branch in one tap"
msgstr "एक ट्यापमै अर्को शाखाको मेनु कपी गर्नुहोस्"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:22
msgid "· 10 items"
msgstr "· 10 आइटम"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:23
msgid "live"
msgstr "लाइभ"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:30
msgid "+ Add from library"
msgstr "+ लाइब्रेरीबाट थप्नुहोस्"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:40
msgid "Lakeside · open now"
msgstr "लेकसाइड · अहिले खुला"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:52
msgid "Branded Menu"
msgstr "ब्रान्डेड मेनु"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:53
msgid "Your own address. Your own look."
msgstr "आफ्नै ठेगाना। आफ्नै रूप।"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:54
msgid ""
"Every venue gets its own subdomain — <span class=\"text-ink font-"
"medium\">your.gaamos.io</span> — with your logo, your colors, your menu. "
"Guests scan and browse instantly in the browser. No app store, no sign-up, "
"no friction."
msgstr ""
"हरेक स्थलले आफ्नै सबडोमेन पाउँछ — <span class=\"text-ink font-"
"medium\">your.gaamos.io</span> — तपाईंकै लोगो, रङ र मेनुसहित। पाहुनाहरूले ब्राउजरमै "
"तुरुन्तै स्क्यान गरेर हेर्छन्। न एप स्टोर, न साइन-अप, न झन्झट।"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:62
msgid "Live Orders"
msgstr "लाइभ अर्डर"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:63
msgid "Orders land the second guests tap \"Place order\""
msgstr "पाहुनाले \"अर्डर गर्नुहोस्\" थिचेकै सेकेन्डमा अर्डर आइपुग्छ"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:64
msgid ""
"No shouting across the room, no lost paper slips. Every order hits your live "
"queue instantly — table or takeaway — and moves from <span class=\"mk-badge-"
"new\">New</span> to <span class=\"mk-badge-served\">Served</span> with one "
"tap."
msgstr ""
"कोठाभरि कराउनु पर्दैन, कागजका पुर्जा हराउँदैनन्। हरेक अर्डर — टेबल होस् वा टेकअवे — तुरुन्तै "
"तपाईंको लाइभ लाइनमा आइपुग्छ र एक ट्यापमै <span class=\"mk-badge-new\">नयाँ</"
"span>बाट <span class=\"mk-badge-served\">सर्भ भयो</span>मा सर्छ।"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:67
msgid "Live queue"
msgstr "लाइभ लाइन"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:67
msgid "· updates in real time"
msgstr "· वास्तविक समयमा अपडेट हुन्छ"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:81
msgid "Table QRs · 1–12"
msgstr "टेबल QR · 1–12"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:81
msgid "↓ Download all (PDF)"
msgstr "↓ सबै डाउनलोड गर्नुहोस् (PDF)"

