#, python-format
msgid "Table %(t)s"
msgstr "टेबल %(t)s"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:89
msgid "QR Codes"
msgstr "QR कोडहरू"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:90
msgid "A QR for the door, or one for every table"
msgstr "ढोकाका लागि एउटा QR, वा हरेक टेबलका लागि एउटा"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:91
msgid ""
"Generate a single venue code or a whole range of table codes in seconds. "
"Download them all as one print-ready PDF, stick them on tables, and you're "
"taking orders. Table QRs tell you exactly where each order came from."
msgstr ""
"सेकेन्डमै एउटा स्थल-कोड वा टेबल-कोडहरूको पूरै दायरा बनाउनुहोस्। सबैलाई एउटै छाप्न तयार PDF "
"मा डाउनलोड गर्नुहोस्, टेबलमा टाँस्नुहोस्, अनि अर्डर लिन थाल्नुहोस्। टेबल QR ले हरेक अर्डर कुन "
"टेबलबाट आयो भन्ने ठ्याक्कै बताउँछ।"

#: templates/marketing/_final_cta.html:4
msgid "Your guests are already holding the menu"
msgstr "तपाईंका पाहुनाको हातमा मेनु पहिल्यै छ"

#: templates/marketing/_final_cta.html:5
msgid "It's their phone. Put your menu on it tonight — live in minutes."
msgstr "त्यो उनीहरूकै फोन हो। आजै राति आफ्नो मेनु त्यसमा राख्नुहोस् — मिनेटमै लाइभ।"

#: templates/marketing/_final_cta.html:7
msgid "Plans from Rs 3,000 a month — cancel anytime"
msgstr "योजना महिनाको रु ३,००० देखि — जहिले पनि रद्द गर्न सकिन्छ"

#: templates/marketing/_footer.html:6
msgid ""
"QR menus and live orders for cafés, restaurants and bars. Your venue at "
"<span class=\"text-white\">your.gaamos.io</span>."
msgstr ""
"क्याफे, रेस्टुरेन्ट र बारका लागि QR मेनु र लाइभ अर्डर। तपाईंको स्थल <span class=\"text-"
"white\">your.gaamos.io</span> मा।"

