#: templates/marketing/_multibranch.html:6
msgid "Every location. One dashboard."
msgstr "हरेक स्थान। एउटै ड्यासबोर्ड।"

#: templates/marketing/_multibranch.html:7
msgid ""
"Run two branches or twenty. Each gets its own menu, its own QR codes, and "
"its own orders — while you watch everything from a single screen. Clone a "
"menu to a new branch and open the doors the same day."
msgstr ""
"दुई शाखा चलाउनुहोस् वा बीस। हरेकको आफ्नै मेनु, आफ्नै QR कोड र आफ्नै अर्डर हुन्छ — तपाईं भने "
"सबै एउटै स्क्रिनबाट हेर्नुहुन्छ। नयाँ शाखामा मेनु कपी गर्नुहोस् र त्यही दिन ढोका खोल्नुहोस्।"

#: templates/marketing/_multibranch.html:9
